Class SafraTreeTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.SafraTreeTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NBA2DAResult<SafraTree>

    public class SafraTreeTemplate
extends java.lang.Object
implements NBA2DAResult<SafraTree>
    A SafraTreeTemplate consists of a SafraTree and two BitSets, one containing the names of nodes that may be renamed and on containing the names that are not allowed in the tree.
